    dcterms:identifier "f7637daf-b71b-4ced-8b54-888c21a4ed22";
    rdfs:label "Technology Node Group";
    skos:altLabel "Node; Technology Node";
    dcterms:description "A Technology Node Group is a collection of Nodes with similar properties. For SC4EU, all possible Nodes have been segmented into 5 Technology Node Groups (short: Above180nm, Under180nm, Under65nm, Under28nm and Under7nm). As a consequence, all Fabs have been segmented in Technology Node Groups..";
