    rdfs:label "End  Market Demand";
    skos:altLabel "EMD; Demand Endmarket; True Demand";
    dcterms:description "End Market Demand (EMD) is the wish of consumers to buy products. It can be considered the end of the Supply Chain. EMD pulls product out of the chain. EMD is also referred to as True Demand.";
